org.apache.zeppelin.client

类 ZSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zeppelin.client.ZSession

  • public class ZSession
extends java.lang.Object
    Each ZSession represent one interpreter process, you can start/stop it, and execute/submit/cancel code. There's no Zeppelin concept(like note/paragraph) in ZSession.
